                     <interp inst="t18370403-1032-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18370403-1032-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for a misdemeanor.</rs>
